                                            A big update for the popular streaming and recording tool.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>OBS Studio is one of the most popular ways to broadcast a livestream or record your screen, and a new major update is rolling out. OBS Studio 32 is now available with a new default video recording option, improvements for RTX graphics cards, better plugin management, and more.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 17:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/obs-studio-32-has-arrived-heres-whats-new/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[8 of My Favorite Comfort Movies for Rainy Days]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/movies-that-were-made-for-rainy-days/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Faisal Rasool]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/collage-of-movie-characters-framed-in-film-strips-against-a-rainy-glass-background-featuring-the-secret-life-of-walter-mitty-paddington-little-miss-sunshine-and-her.png" length="2482" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Streaming]]></category><category><![CDATA[ Movies]]></category><category><![CDATA[Streaming]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            A good rainy-day movie will feel like a warm blanket or offer a nice escape till the clouds clear.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>With the fall months upon us and the weather starting to do more questionable things, you might be thinking a bit more about staying inside. Here are some of my comfort films that I’ve seen many, many times, and found their vibe just perfectly complements a cold or rainy day.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 17:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/movies-that-were-made-for-rainy-days/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[How to Edit Environment Variables on Windows 10 or 11]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/787217/how-to-edit-environment-variables-on-windows-10-or-11/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Nick Lewis]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/computer-monitor-showing-the-windows-environment-variables-editor-with-an-open-dialog-for-editing-a-system-variable.png" length="1071" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Windows]]></category><category><![CDATA[Windows 11]]></category><category><![CDATA[Windows 10]]></category><category><![CDATA[Programming]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Use Environment Variables to streamline your scripts and make using command-line applications easier. 
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Editing your PC's environment variables can save you time in Command Prompt and make your scripts more concise. It also lets you customize where Windows stores certain files. This is what you need to know about getting started adding, editing, or removing entries from your Environment Variables on Windows.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 17:15:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/787217/how-to-edit-environment-variables-on-windows-10-or-11/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[You Can Now Tell Google Photos How to Edit a Photo for You]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/you-can-now-tell-google-photos-how-to-edit-a-photo-for-you/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Joe Fedewa]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/blogpost-header_color-version-2096x1182.png" length="23345" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Google Photos]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Transform your photos with simple voice or text commands.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Learning the ins and outs of editing can help you transform good photos into great photos, but not everyone has spent the time gathering those skills. Google is always trying to make it easier for people to make their photos shine, and now there’s a new conversational way to do it.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 17:04:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/you-can-now-tell-google-photos-how-to-edit-a-photo-for-you/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[The Used Hybrid Under $30K That Stands Out for Safety and Efficiency]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/used-hybrid-under-30000-that-stands-out-for-safety-and-efficiency/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Adam Gray]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/2024_prius_limited_reservoirblue_008.jpg" length="91" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Automotive]]></category><category><![CDATA[Hybrid Cars]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            This one-year-old used hybrid is a safe, efficient choice that won’t break the bank.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>The <a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/10-year-old-hybrid-more-reliable-than-new-rivals/" target="_blank">Toyota Prius</a> might not be the flashiest car on the lot, but it’s still a big deal for <a href="https://www.howtogeek.com/tag/toyota/" target="_blank">Toyota</a>. Over the years, it’s built a reputation for being super efficient, affordable, and safe—all without fuss.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 17:00:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/used-hybrid-under-30000-that-stands-out-for-safety-and-efficiency/</guid></item>                                                                <item><title><![CDATA[Uber Has a Way to Make Repeat Rides Cheaper]]></title><link>https://www.howtogeek.com/uber-has-a-way-to-make-repeat-rides-cheaper/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Jorge A. Aguilar]]></dc:creator><enclosure url="https://static0.howtogeekimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/a-man-looking-at-his-uber-app-next-to-a-car-with-the-uber-logo-on-it.jpg" length="202" type="image/jpeg"/><category><![CDATA[Android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apps & Web Apps]]></category><description><![CDATA[
                                            Scheduling rides can be a lot cheaper than you think.
                                        ]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[
                                                                                                                                    <p>Uber has just announced a new feature called Prepaid Pass, which is a new way for you to save money on your regular rides by paying for them upfront. This is a much cheaper alternative because it is a flat rate, instead of being affected by other factors.</p>                    ]]></content:encoded><pubDate>Tue, 23 Sep 2025 16:40:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.howtogeek.com/uber-has-a-way-to-make-repeat-rides-cheaper/</guid></item></channel>
